Data-handling notice
--------------------

This repository's `guardian/forgetful/` subsystem (the Forgetful Agent) is
designed to process and redact personally identifying information (PII) and
protected health information (PHI) from content before it is published. The
agent itself retains no values from processed content; it emits a signed
manifest listing only the TYPES and COUNTS of detections per file, never
the detected values.

Any content derived from patient records, research subjects, or other
identifiable source material MUST pass through the Forgetful Agent before
landing on a public branch. See `FORKING.md` and `docs/ingest.md` for the
full data-handling discipline.
